title: Audi MMI 3G Europe 2015-2016 (4G0 919 884 R 5.21.2)
description:
Map databases version 2015-2016 (5.21.2)for MMI 3G Basic (No HDD, no 3D, no Joystick)

- Includes Firmware Upgrade for MMI 3G Basic to Version K0257
- Includes two DVDs
- Includes Activator for BNav_EU_K0257_9_D1 to run the map databases


DVD1 - Western Europe:

Germany, Liechtenstein, Austria, Switzerland, Andorra, Belgium, France, Gibraltar, Great Britain, Ireland, Luxembourg, Monaco, Netherlands, Portugal, Spain

DVD2 - Eastern Europe: 

Germany, Liechtenstein, Austria, Switzerland, Albania, Bosnia-Herzegovina, Bulgaria, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, Greece, Italy, Croatia, Corsica, Kosovo, Latvia, Lithuania, Macedonia, Moldavia, Montenegro, Norway, Poland, Romania, Russia, San Marino, Sweden, Serbia, Slovakia, Slovenia, Czech Republic, Ukraine, Hungary, Vatican City, Belarus
